  "description": "Fixes the bug that Fortune doesn't work on Amethyst Clusters if applied on pickaxes from mods.",
  "body": "<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Amethysts of Fortune</strong></h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>That mod fixes the bug that Fortune doesn't work on Amethyst Clusters if applied on pickaxes from mods.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Subscribe on mod's platforms:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/TpP4vAMDgb\">Discord Server</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@unknownraccooneternaltales4940\">YouTube</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a title=\"Telegramm channel\" href=\"https://t.me/eternal_tales_news\">Telegram channel</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://eternaltales.wiki.gg/wiki/Eternal_Tales_Wiki\">Wiki</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://vk.com/eternal_tales\">VK (Russian)&nbsp;</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/622/155/2023-02-14_17.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"581\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>You can turn off Fortune for amethysts by changing /gamerule amethystFortune false.</strong></p>",
